      <title>印度国营炼油厂可能加剧对委内瑞拉石油的竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/indian-state-refiners-may-sharpen-competition-for-venezuelan-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府控制的炼油厂正与亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼(Mukesh Ambani)的信实工业有限公司(Reliance Industries Ltd.)一起寻求购买委内瑞拉原油，从而加剧了与中国用户对折扣桶的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/indian-state-refiners-may-sharpen-competition-for-venezuelan-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 07:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
